overview: YOUNG & BEAUTIFUL. This series brings together nubile newcomers who love to experiment. Featured cover girl Alexis Tae is a college coed from a rich family, and now that she's off in the big city she's looking for an older man to teach her some things she cant learn in class. Allie Nicole, Little Dragon, and Eva Elfie are all here to show you how todays young women like their action. Startling stories, ritzy settings, and intense-as-fuck action.
title: Young & Beautiful 11
